and what is it that you do exactly?

42
00:02:09,013 --> 00:02:11,975
So I'll briefly cover what narrative design is and what it isn't,

43
00:02:12,295 --> 00:02:14,236
and which skills you might already have

44
00:02:14,757 --> 00:02:18,018
that would help you become one even without any narrative experience.

45
00:02:19,099 --> 00:02:22,761
As with all game dev, getting your foot in the door is the hardest part.

46
00:02:22,841 --> 00:02:26,023
