you can stack the deck in your favor to get them.

48
00:02:29,472 --> 00:02:32,254
or even convince a studio to create the job you want.

49
00:02:32,954 --> 00:02:35,575
So I hope you'll walk a day knowing that you can take the plunge

50
00:02:36,275 --> 00:02:39,377
and successfully transition into narrative design from another discipline

51
00:02:39,457 --> 00:02:43,279
by making your existing expertise into your unique selling point,

52
00:02:43,979 --> 00:02:47,061
and that if you love storytelling, you can get paid to do it.

53
